Description: This R package provides learning content creators with generation of XML files for Tests and Tasks according to QTI information model v. 2.1. The sources of data for Test/Task content can be Rmd/md templates or objects of S4-classes, created in R environment. This package generates all basic types of tasks and has full set of attributes for tests customisation.
